description: Easy-byte-coder is a non-invasive bytecode injection framework based on JVM. Java application developers can implement bytecode injection quickly, without caring about the underlying instrument principle and implementation details. Easy-byte-coder provides AOP ability in the form of plugin. Static waving (Agent) and dynamic waving (Attach) make plugin development easy.
Python app implements a client (victim) and server (attacker) scripts with session (multi-client)
